snippet.title: September 1999 | Now on Steam!
snippet.description:
For those of you lovely people who like to keep their games in one place, September 1999 is now also on Steam! And it's free! 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/952250/SEPTEMBER_1999/


You can also find me on Twitter, Facebook and Patreon:
https://www.facebook.com/98demake
https://twitter.com/98demake
https://www.patreon.com/98demake

If you would like to contact me for some reason, you can do that at: 98demake (at) gmail.com
